    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Winter witch baronesses are members of Irrisen\u2019s aristocracy who rule towns and villages throughout the nation. As a baroness (or sometimes countess depending on her rank), a winter witch reports to the ruler of her province. Some baronesses and countesses treat their subjects better than others, but across the board they are unsympathetic, short-tempered, and cruel."
        }
    ],
